{"id":300584,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/广州日报-南京饿死幼女：趴马桶吃粪便-被发现时/","date":"2013-06-24T06:57:46Z","modified":"2013-06-24T06:57:46Z","title":"广州日报 | 南京饿死幼女：趴马桶吃粪便 被发现时已风干","content":"<p>@广州日报：【南京幼女饿死真相】6.21民警在南京江宁泉水新村发现两个女孩死在家里，震惊了全国。记者@记者崔永利 爆孩子饿死真相：孩子整夜拍着门喊着妈妈；饿得趴在马桶里吃粪便；尿不湿不换导致下身溃烂”&#8230;..“孩子们光着屁股，一次次的拍着窗户”，满脸都是粪便！最后孩子抱出来的时候都已经已经风干了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/20130624125508d65d2.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-300586\" alt=\"20130624125508d65d2\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/20130624125508d65d2.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"817\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/20130624125508d65d2.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/20130624125508d65d2-161x300.jpg 161w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/201306241255118b020.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-300587\" alt=\"201306241255118b020\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/201306241255118b020.jpg\" width=\"440\" height=\"1183\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/2013062412551351ec4.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-300588\" alt=\"2013062412551351ec4\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/2013062412551351ec4.jpg\" width=\"423\" height=\"1183\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/2013062412551351ec4.jpg 423w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/2013062412551351ec4-107x300.jpg 107w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/2013062412551351ec4-366x1024.jpg 366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 423px) 100vw, 423px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/2013062412551563431.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-300589\" alt=\"2013062412551563431\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/06/2013062412551563431.jpg\